data.description:
YOUR CHANCE TO LIVE IN AN ELITE 6TH FLOOR UNIT IN THE MUCH SOUGHT AFTER ENVY RESIDENCES IN OLD TOWN SCOTTSDALE!!
This gorgeous unit feature highly upgraded wide plank wood floors, Poggenpohl cabinetry, Quartz countertops, Bosch Stainless steel
appliances with a waterfall island and designer tiled gas fireplace feature, spa like baths with unbelievable A+ views of Camelback Mtn and
Sunsets and a spacious balcony plumbed for a gas grill! ENVY boasts absolutely state of the art amenities including a 4000 sq ft Fitness
Facility, swanky Black Label Lounge, gorgeous pool and pool lounge area that rivals any Las Vegas resort, underground parking, 24 hr
concierge/security and so much more. MUST SEE, WALKING DISTANCE TO EVERYTHING OLD TOWN SCOTTSDALE HAS TO OFFER.
